ards, devices that meld the traditional knotted strings known as khipus with a written alphabet. Only in the Entablo do we learn that there were multiple khipu boards associated with a single canal-cleaning ritual, or that there were separate khipu records for men and women. The Entablo manuscript furnishes unparalleled insights into Andean rituals, religion, and community history at a historical moment when rural highland communities were changing rapidly.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aQuechua IndiansxReligionxRitualsxTexts2DLC. 0aQuechua IndiansxReligionxRitualsxTexts. 0aQuechua IndianszPeruzSan Pedro de CastaxReligion2DLC. 0aQuechua IndianszPeruzSan Pedro de CastaxReligion. 0aQuechua IndianszPeruzSan Pedro de CastaxRites and ceremonies2DLC. 0aQuechua IndianszPeruzSan Pedro de CastaxRites and ceremonies. 0aQuechua IndianszPeruzSan Pedro de CastaxSocial life and customs2DLC. 0aQuechua IndianszPeruzSan Pedro de CastaxSocial life and customs. 0aQuechua languagexWriting2DLC. 0aQuechua languagexWriting. 0aQuipuzPeruzSan Pedro de Casta2DLC. 0aQuipuzPeruzSan Pedro de Casta. 0aWaterzPeruzSan Pedro de CastaxReligious aspects2DLC. 0aWaterzPeruzSan Pedro de CastaxReligious aspects. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Cultural and Area Studies 2023 Englishz978311131909408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Cultural and Area Studies 2023z978311131812740uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/32542140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781477325438423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.co